---
// Services component - What we do and modular offer stack
---

<section id="services" class="py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-neutral-50">
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
		<!-- Section header -->
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-6">
				What we do
			</h2>
			<p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				Founder-level product strategy meets fast, full-stack execution. We don't just advise—we build.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Modular Offer Stack -->
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 mb-16">
			<!-- Automate Operations -->
			<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-neutral-200">
				<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
					<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900">Automate Operations</h3>
				</div>
				<p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Replace spreadsheets and manual processes with internal tools, workflows, and automation.</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-600 space-y-2">
					<li>Retool dashboards</li>
					<li>CRM to onboarding automation</li>
					<li>Slack/Email alerts</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<!-- Deploy AI Copilots -->
			<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-neutral-200">
				<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
					<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" /><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4" /></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900">Deploy AI Copilots</h3>
				</div>
				<p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">AI-powered assistants that surface answers, streamline decisions, and automate repetitive tasks.</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-600 space-y-2">
					<li>LLM copilots for docs, support, internal ops</li>
					<li>Context-aware workflows</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<!-- Build Decision Tools -->
			<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-neutral-200">
				<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
					<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 17l6-6 4 4 8-8" /></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900">Build Decision Tools</h3>
				</div>
				<p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Real-time dashboards, forecasting tools, and segmentation engines that give teams leverage.</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-600 space-y-2">
					<li>Data apps with dbt, Postgres, Python</li>
					<li>Front-ends for visibility + action</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<!-- Scale Product Systems -->
			<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-neutral-200">
				<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
					<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" /></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900">Scale Product Systems</h3>
				</div>
				<p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Foundational infrastructure, strategy, and fractional leadership to grow with clarity.</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-600 space-y-2">
					<li>GTM system design</li>
					<li>Roadmapping & feedback loops</li>
					<li>Fractional product leadership</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-4">Built with tools that scale: Python, FastAPI, Retool, OpenAI, dbt, Postgres<br/>(We don't reinvent the wheel—we build systems that work inside yours.)</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section> 